.DS_Store
.wrangler/

# instructions/ holds working material that stays out of the repo (drafts,
# audit reports, backlog notes, .docx files). The technical spec is the one
# exception — it's tracked so it can be updated alongside the code it
# describes. Note the pattern must be `instructions/*`, not `instructions/`:
# git will not re-include a file whose parent directory is itself excluded,
# so negating a path inside an excluded directory silently does nothing.
instructions/*
!instructions/postandin-technical-spec.md
